column5: When you go from lakair on the water and you travel under the bridge passed where the dog always fishes there is a lodge to the left hand side the name of which is painted on the cliff Mesquta something can anone help me out with this they have a cabin that is on the cliff facing the water i would like to rent this for 4 days for our anniversery it was 080808 the big 10 and i have been giving the choice of stomping grounds for this grand event Thanks Peter
this place?? never heard or seen it...    here's your casa d'amore
Thanks Cory and Raf  lots of amore and more and more
Very nice cabin, they remodeled the inside a few years ago with pine boards.  You won't be disappointed with the views from the deck.  The lodge owners are great to deal with as well, top notch.  Tom

Thanks for that pic Raf..... Havent been there YET..but certainly remember seeing it and the memory has spooked me...so much we have it on the ...'Are Doin List'  Hope your weekend amore and all,  is just grand pete

Stayed there the last few years and the place is excellent!  Can't say enough good things about it. Be sure to download their 44 page PDF file.  Tons of excellent info in it. Memquisit Visitors Guide Good Luck
I'll be parked out front of the billboard this weekend  Happy Anniversary Pete!
